overview: Welcome to Sell4More.com located at the American Bullion Center, 2334 York Rd. Timonium MD 21093, where you can always SELL 4 MORE! We buy Rare US Coins and coin collections of all types. Sterling Silver items made by Stieff, Kirk, and Tiffany and all 10KT 14KT 18KT Gold Jewelry are also our specialty. We buy US gold and silver eagles and pre 1964 90% silver halves, quarters and dimes. We evaluate pocket and wrist watches, wedding bands, and class rings. We pay the highest daily spot cash price for your gold, coins, and jewelry items in a comfortable and personal environment.
